{
  "texts": [
    "-In Minecraft, item can be put in agent's inventory, chest, or on the ground.",
    "You can use the item in agent's inventory or chest, but you can not use the item on the ground unless you dig it up first.",
    "-The block at lower place should be placed first, and the block at higher place should be placed later.",
    "[x,-60,z] is the lowest place.",
    "For example, if a task is placing block at x -57 z, then y -60, -59 and -58 should be placed first and in order."
  ]
}